    ReplicateBE.jl Documentation

    ReplicateBE.jl is a Julia package providing mixed model solution for replicate designed bioequivalence study. This can be used to obtained results with methods C (random effects with interaction), given by the EMA in Annex I. Statistical model formed with accordance FDA Guidance for Industry: Statistical Approaches to Establishing Bioequivalence, APPENDIX F.
